title: #92Noon! Boudreau/TC&RJ/Leber/ATopics/Coyle/Fleck!
description: Wild coach Bruce Boudreau opens, then Ron Johnson & Tyrone Carter are in studio on Gophers/Vikes...Ben Leber's weekly stop, along with a Super Bowl Story from Osi Umenyiora in the middle hour, PrimeTimePicks/ATopics, then Gophers AD Mark Coyle and coach PJ Fleck each give a segment to a busy Thursday show!
